# <type>([optional scope]): <description>
#
# [Body - optional]
#
# [Footer(s) - optional]
# ---------------------------------------------------------
# Types:
#   feat     : New feature
#   fix      : Bug fix
#   refactor : Code change without a feature or fix
#   perf     : Performance improvement
#   docs     : Documentation only
#   test     : Add or fix tests
#   style    : Code style only; no behavior change
#   chore    : Build, dependencies, tooling, or non-src/non-test changes
# ---------------------------------------------------------
# Rules:
#   - Description: Imperative, lowercase, no period; target ≤50 chars, max 72
#   - Body: Explain why, not what; omit if obvious; wrap at 72 chars; '-' bullets
#   - Footer: Breaking changes or issue refs only (e.g. Closes #12)
#   - Never: AI attribution, I/we, or "This commit does"
# ---------------------------------------------------------